'''虹膜色素缺陷瘤'''，又称为'''立舍瘤'''（'''Lisch nodule'''），是指[[虹膜|虹膜]]树突状[[黑色素细胞|黑色素细胞]]的色素[[错构瘤|错构瘤]]结节性聚合<ref>{{cite web |title=Free Medicla Textbook |chapter=151 |url=http://medtextfree.wordpress.com/2011/01/20/chapter-151-uveal-nevus/ |accessdate=20 October 2011 |archive-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019071608/https://medtextfree.wordpress.com/2011/01/20/chapter-151-uveal-nevus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=robbins7>{{Citation | author=Kumar, Vinay; Fausto, Nelson; Fausto, Nelso; Robbins, Stanley L.; Abbas, Abul K.; Cotran, Ramzi S.  | title=Robbins and Cotran Pathologic Basis of Disease | year=2005 | edition=7th| publisher=Elsevier Saunders | location=Philadelphia, Pa. | isbn=0-7216-0187-1 | page=169}}</ref>。疾病由[[奥地利|奥地利]][[眼科学|眼科医生]]卡尔·立舍（Karl Lisch，1907年-1999年）在1937年首先提出并以他的姓氏命名<ref name=Lukacs1997>{{citation | author = Lukacs, Andreas; Junk, Anna K.; Fritz, Stefani H.; Kampik, Anselm; Georg, Schirren Carl; Plewig, Gerd | year = 1997 | title = Lisch nodules. Markers of neurofibromatosis 1 and immunohistochemical references for neuroectodermal differentiation | journal = Hautarzt | volume = 48 | issue = 1 | pages = 38–41 | doi = 10.1007/s001050050544 | url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/gl49atrh5lff517r/?p=76057c4c0e29493ca59de8093e27009e | pmid = 9132386 | accessdate = 2011-12-02 | archive-date = 2020-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200125052128/http://www.springerlink.com/content/gl49atrh5lff517r/?p=76057c4c0e29493ca59de8093e27009e | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

虹膜色素缺陷瘤常见于[[Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病|Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病]]，超过94％的患者都是在六岁之后出现结节<ref name=robbins7 />。结节从虹膜表面突出，边缘清楚，棕黄色<ref name=Richetta2004>{{citation | author = Richetta, A.; Giustini, A.; Recupero, S. M.; Pezza, M.; Carlomagno, C.; Amoruso, G.; Calvieri, S. | year = 2004 | title = Lisch nodules of the iris in neurofibromatosis type 1 | journal = Journal of the European Academy of Dermatology and Venerology | volume = 18 | issue = 3 | pages = 342–4 | doi = 10.1111/j.1468-3083.2004.00915.x | url = http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/fulltext/118788235/PDFSTART | pmid = 15096151 | accessdate = 2011-12-02 | archive-date = 2020-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200125052129/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/fulltext/118788235/PDFSTART | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，椭圆形或圆形，类似圆顶状丘疹。这些结节可以在[[裂隙灯|裂隙灯]]检查中被发现<ref name=Richetta2004 />，通常不影响视力，但对诊断某些疾病如Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病很有帮助<ref name=robbins7 />。[[免疫组织化学|免疫组织化学]]染色显示[[波形蛋白|波形蛋白]]和[[S-100蛋白|S-100蛋白]]阳性，暗示其起源于[[胚胎|胚胎]][[外胚层|外胚层]]<ref name=Lukacs1997/>，但准确的起源和结构现在仍存在争议<ref name=Richetta2004 />。在[[Ⅱ型神经纤维瘤病|Ⅱ型神经纤维瘤病]]没有发现虹膜色素缺陷瘤。

